cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.CC, cs.SI, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with information theory and communication, specifically the wiretap channel. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) is the most likely category. The paper also involves cryptography and security, which suggests cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as another likely category. The use of the Chernoff-Cramer bound indicates cs.CC (Computational Complexity) as a possible category. The paper also involves signal processing and coding, which suggests cs.SI (Signal Processing) and cs.MM (Multimedia) as possible categories.
